{
  "texts": [
    "Each white paper also contains references, which need to be deleted to prevent our Q&A system from mixing the titles of works cited with the evidence-base summarized in the document.",
    "We thus automatically search for a reference Sec.",
    "header and remove all content therein.",
    "This produces a text file, which we ultimately seek to pass onto GPT along with questions.",
    "GPT performs a natural language understanding task known as Open Domain Question Answering (ODQA) (Siriwardhana et al., 2023)."
  ]
}